  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Anomalous Material",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "异常材料",
    "TencentChinese": "异常材料",
    "TraditionalChinese": "異常材料"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "This oily, unsettling liquid leaks from the circuitry of <span class=\"name name-special\">Sentinels</span>.<br><br>Prized by the <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Vy'keen</span>, Pugneum is thought to share some essential properties with <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nanites</span>. It hums in a sinister fashion upon contact with organic matter.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这种油腻、令人不安的液体从<span class=\"name name-special\">护卫</span>的电路中渗漏出来。<br><br>受<span class=\"name name-fuel\">维吉恩</span>广泛称赞的普茵与<span class=\"name name-technology\">纳米星团</span>在一些本质上有异曲同工之妙。它与有机物接触时会发出诡异的嗡嗡声。",
    "TencentChinese": "这种油腻、令人不安的液体从<span class=\"name name-special\">护卫</span>的电路中渗漏出来。<br><br>受<span class=\"name name-fuel\">维吉恩</span>广泛称赞的普茵与<span class=\"name name-technology\">纳米星团</span>在一些本质上有异曲同工之妙。它与有机物接触时会发出诡异的嗡嗡声。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這種不穩定的油性液體，是從<span class=\"name name-special\">巡警</span>電路滲出的物質。<br><br>被<span class=\"name name-fuel\">維金族</span>視為珍寶的搏元素，一般認為本質與<span class=\"name name-technology\">奈米機群</span>相似。與有機物質接觸時，會發出邪惡的低吟。"
  },
